answers.body_markdown:
Thats the Wrong way! you must use DTO for that!

for Example you have:

    @Entity
    @Table(name = &quot;CaribbeanCountry&quot;, schema = &quot;table&quot;)
    public class CaribbeanCountryEntity {
      private String county;
      private String city;
      ...
    }

Then you have a DTO like:

     public class CaribbeanCountryEntityDTO {
          private String county;
          private String city;
          ...
          private String customthink;

        }

After that you must Copy (for that you can use a Mapper like modelMapper) Object to the DTO object und you must then return the DTO custom object.

